# 1
# Weak form
Source: a:91
Vetted: s
Judgment: g
Phenomena: pronouns
n mi
n         mi
1s.NOM.WK know
'I know'

# 2
# Strong form
# Adapted from a:91
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgment: g
Phenomena: pronouns
maa mi
maa        mi
1s.NOM.STR know
'I, for one, know'

# 3
# Weak form
# Adapted from a:114
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgement: g
Phenomena: pronouns
fo boɔro la koɔraa
fo        boɔ-ro    la   koɔraa
2s.NOM.WK love-IPFV FACT farmer
'you love a farmer'

# 4
# Strong form
# Adapted from a:114
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgement: g
Phenomena: pronouns
foo boɔro koɔraa
foo        boɔ-ro    koɔraa
2s.NOM.STR love-IPFV farmer
'you, in particular, might love a farmer'

