'a farmer might die'

# 2
# Adapted from a:41
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgment: g
Phenomena: determiners
a koɔraa kpie
a   koɔraa kpi-e
DEF farmer die-PERF.INTR
'the farmer might die'

# 3
# Adapted from a:41
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgment: g
Phenomena: determiners
koɔraa kanga kpie
koɔraa kanga kpi-e
farmer SPC   die-PERF.INTR
'a certain farmer dies'

# 4
# Adapted from a:41
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgment: u
Phenomena: determiners
kanga koɔraa kpie
kanga      koɔraa kpi-e
SPEC farmer die-PERF.INTR
'a certain farmer dies'

# 5
# Adapted from a:41
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgment: g
Phenomena: determiners
mine kɔribɔ kpie
mine kɔr-ibɔ   kpi-e
